Package controller.controllermessage

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ControllerMessage
    This class represents every message guiding the evolution of the game.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PickActionMessage
    This class is an implementation of ControllerMessage and is used when an action can be chosen
    PickPowerupMessage
    This class is an implementation of ControllerMessage and is used when a powerUp can be chosen
    PickTargetMessage
    This class is an implementation of ControllerMessage and is used when a target can be chosen
    PickWeaponMessage
    This class is an implementation of ControllerMessage and is used when a weapon can be chosen
    RollbackMessage
    This class is an implementation of ControllerMessage and is used when a rollback must be done (no actions are available)
    StringChoiceMessage
    This class is an implementation of ControllerMessage and is used when a srting can be chosen
    WaitMessage
    This class is an implementation of ControllerMessage and is used when no choices can be done
